 Act to authorize a board of a school district to adopt policies regarding students who are registered sex offenders, and to declare an emergency. Be it enacted by the Legislature of the State of South Dakota: Section 1. That chapter 13-28 be amended with a NEW SECTION: A board of a school district may adopt a policy that requires a student who is registered as a sex offender, pursuant to \u00a7 22-24B-2, to receive instruction through remote or distance learning or an alternative educational program. Section 2. Whereas, this Act is necessary for the support of the state government and its existing public institutions, an emergency is hereby declared to exist, and this Act shall be in full force and effect from and after its passage and approval."}], "amendments": [], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 24290, "action_date": "2023-01-30T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 246905, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/246905.pdf", "status_text": "First read in Senate and referred to", "journal_page": 136, "committee_id_action": 1183, "committee_id_assigned": 1174, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 24290, "action_date": "2023-02-16T08:15:00-06:00", "document_id": 249427, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/249427.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for hearing", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 1174, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 24290, "action_date": "2023-02-16T08:15:00-06:00", "document_id": 249428, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/249428.pdf", "status_text": "Motion to amend", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 1174, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 24290, "action_date": "2023-02-16T08:15:00-06:00", "document_id": 249428, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/249428.pdf", "status_text": "Do Pass Amended", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 1